title: As Blood Runs Black - Ground Zero
description:
As Blood Runs Black is an American deathcore band from Los Angeles, California.[2] They have released two albums. Their first album, Allegiance, was released on June 6, 2006.[3] Their second album, Instinct, was released on March 15, 2011.[4] Instinct reached number 1 on the Billboard Heatseakers Albums chart and number 111 on the Billboard 200 for the week of April 2, 2011.[5] On June 30, 2013, As Blood Runs Black announced that they will be self-releasing their newest album with the help of crowdfunding via IndieGoGo.
